            "id": 338909376627642,
            "definition": {
                "type": "note",
                "content": "### About This Dashboard  \n\nWelcome to your Reflectiz **Web Exposure Alerts Dashboard**, your centralized hub for an overview of your website security risk. This dashboard offers actionable insights based on the Reflectiz Alert System to help you manage and secure your websites effectively.  \n\n**To get the most accurate and relevant insights**:  \n1. **Filter the dashboard by a specific site and scan** to narrow the data to your desired site.  \n1. In the \"Website Scan Overview\" under the \"Last Scan Per Site\" table, select the latest scan for you desired site.\n1. Select \"Template Variables\" and set both the `reflectiz.site` & `reflectiz.scan` variables.\n1. Optional: Select the host using the filter at the top left of the dashboard. By selecting a Datadog host, your can review risks associated with any website running on that host.\n\n### About the Alert Feature  \n\nThe Reflectiz Platform regularly scans your website monitoring all first, third, and fourth-party applications. It detects vulnerabilities and risks in your online ecosystem, providing complete visibility over your web threat exposure surface. It effectively prioritizes and remediates risks and compliance issues.\n\nFor more in-depth analysis and additional features, visit the [Reflectiz Platform](https://dashboard.reflectiz.com/main/dashboard).",
                "background_color": "white",
                "font_size": "14",
                "text_align": "left",
                "vertical_align": "top",
                "show_tick": false,
                "tick_pos": "50%",
                "tick_edge": "left",
                "has_padding": true
            },
            "layout": {
                "x": 0,
                "y": 2,
                "width": 6,
                "height": 5
            }
        },
